<br>
Though I never really let it bother me until a monk friend of mine who was the same level told me to either taunt better (ok it has a 4 second refresh, want me to push it harder) or let him tank cause he didn't want to FD all the time. I was level 56 at the time in chardok. That really pissed me off. Neither of us had spectacular gear and ever since then it has only gotten worse. <br>
<br>
So any monks reading this, sorry if I am less than sympathetic with you. Blah you can't solo now, warriors never could. All I have to say to the monks is STFU!<br>
